The global toothpaste tablets market is expected to witness significant growth by 2028. One of the key factors driving this growth is the increasing consumer shift towards sustainable and eco-friendly oral care products. The demand for toothpaste tablets is rising as they are considered to have lower environmental impact compared to traditional toothpaste tubes, which contribute to plastic waste. Additionally, the convenience of using toothpaste tablets while traveling is also boosting market growth.

